  "instructions": [
    "Heat claypot to 450 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "Mix flour and salt in a bowl.",
    "Gradually add water to create a dough.",
    "Knead dough for 5 minutes.",
    "Let dough rest for 30 minutes.",
    "Heat 1 tablespoon of olive oil in claypot. ",
    "Divide dough into 6 equal pieces.",
    "Shape each piece into a ball and then flatten into a disc.",
    "Place the discs in the claypot, leaving 1 inch gap between each disc.",
    "Bake for 15 minutes or until golden brown.",
    "Remove from heat and let cool for 5 minutes.",
    "Crush the baked discs into a pilaf-like texture.",
    "Mix in paprika and garlic powder.",
    "Serve warm."
